{"word":"πιλέω","slug":"πιλέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>πιλέω</b></el> <el>(πῑλέω,) ( φυτ. <el>-ήσω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πῖλος'><el>πῖλος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to compress wool</i>, <el>πιληθεὶς πέτασος</el> a <i>felt</i> hat, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be close pressed, kneaded</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}